QuicksilverDB Repository Log
================================================================================
10/25: Changes for enabling remote debugging using Eclipse added.

	- To start remote debugging, just start hive with service parameter 
	  'cliWithRemoteDebugger'. ie.
	    > $HIVE_HOME/bin/hive --service cliWithRemoteDebugger
	- Now you can connect to hive through Eclipse on port 8001.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
10/7: Forked out current Hive and Hadoop branches.
